                <h1 class="entry-title">Sliding doors, cosa sarebbe successo a Montella se Cutrone non avesse segnato?</h1>

                

                <div class="td-module-meta-info">
                    <div class="td-post-author-name"><div class="td-author-by">Di</div> <a href="https://www.milannews24.com/author/redazione/">Redazione Milan News 24</a><div class="td-author-line"> - </div> </div>                    <span class="td-post-date"><time class="entry-date updated td-module-date" datetime="2017-09-29T16:38:54+00:00" >29 settembre 2017</time></span>                                                        </div>

            </header>

        </div>

        

        <div class="td-post-content">

        <div class="td-post-featured-image"><figure><img width="696" height="391" class="entry-thumb" src="https://www.milannews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/montella-milan-settembre-2017.jpg" srcset="https://www.milannews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/montella-milan-settembre-2017.jpg 696w, https://www.milannews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/montella-milan-settembre-2017-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.milannews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/montella-milan-settembre-2017-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.milannews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/montella-milan-settembre-2017-32x18.jpg 32w" sizes="(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px" alt="Vincenzo Montella" title="montella-milan-settembre-2017"/><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">&copy; foto www.imagephotoagency.it</figcaption></figure></div>
        <div class="_h8t">
<div class="_5wd9 direction_ltr">
<div class="_5wde _n4o">
<div class="_5w1r _3_om _5wdf">
<div class="_4gx_">
<h2>Cutrone con la sua rete è riuscito a salvare Montella dalla terza brutta figura stagionale, ma come sarebbe andata se il numero 63 non avesse realizzato il 3 a 2?</h2>





<!-- Mediamatic | Mobile - 300x169 | 469 & 470 -->
